{"tid":815344,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗葡軍隊友：沒有C朗完全無礙球隊發揮","createTime":"2018-09-12T03:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T10:27:30.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa379d8079691fdca231115bd7ce088656b9001","tid":815344,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】祖雲達斯球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）雖缺席今期葡萄牙隊比賽，主帥費蘭度山度士藉此試驗換血成效，C朗球會隊友祖奧簡斯路更揚言有準備交接。<br />\n<br />\n意大利隊昨仗20年來首次沒有班霸祖雲達斯球員正選上陣，反觀葡萄牙在C朗缺陣下仍有祖奧簡斯路出戰，這名「斑馬軍」右閘賽後說：「C朗無疑是我們重要一員，但沒有他，球隊還保持着高水平。我們這一輩會在此迎接這轉變。」第101次代表葡軍的35歲老將比比（圖左）亦讚揚後輩表現令人鼓舞。"},{"pid":"0d24108019ac2139355091ec6f8a4a9d498f865c","tid":815344,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:08:15.000Z","msg":"沒有朗 怎敢說心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43e5a2c4e711a7a6fc79f206a9415de427f6d57","tid":815344,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0d24108019ac2139355091ec6f8a4a9d498f865c","tid":815344,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:08:15.000Z","msg":"沒有朗 怎敢說心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:09:45.000Z","msg":"賤朗粉 怎敢說心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁岩音"},{"pid":"67b52bf1537d659f80886a19db03286f1229a622","tid":815344,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d43e5a2c4e711a7a6fc79f206a9415de427f6d57","tid":815344,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0d24108019ac2139355091ec6f8a4a9d498f865c","tid":815344,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:08:15.000Z","msg":"沒有朗 怎敢說心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:09:45.000Z","msg":"賤朗粉 怎敢說心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁岩音"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:10:55.0